d%20nature%20and%20stunning%20views%20of%20the%20Cetina%20river%20canyon.%20One%20of%20the%20guide%20hooks%20you%20up%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20each%20wire%2C%20while%20the%20other%20one%20waits%20for%20you%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20wire.%20That%20is%20the%20system%20to%20pass%20all%20eight%20wires.%0D%0A%0D%0AThe%20finish%20point%20of%20a%20zipline%20tour%20is%20located%2050m%20from%20the%20road%2C%20and%20there%20is%20our%20van%20waiting%20to%20take%20you%20back%20to%20Omis.%0D%0A%0D%0AYou%20can%20also%20go%20by%20your%20vehicle%20from%20Omis%20and%20leave%20it%20near%20the%20finish%20point%20of%20the%20Zipline%20polygone%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20restaurant%20Kastil%20Slanica%2C%20where%20you%20can%20have%20a%20meal%20afterwards.%3C%2Ffonts%3E%0D%0A%3Cbr%2F%3E%0D%0A%3Cfont%20style%3D%22font-size%3A10px%22%3EQuelle%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fzipline-croatia.com%2Factive-holidays-omis-croatia%2F%22%3Ehttp%3A%2F%2Fzipline-croatia.com%2Factive-holidays-omis-croatia%2F%3C%2Fa%3E&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bsubtitle_position%5D=subtitle-bottom&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bclass%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_label_primary%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_url_primary%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_url_primary_target_blank%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_label_secondary%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_url_secondary%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Bdata%5D%5Bcall_to_url_secondary_target_blank%5D=&rows%5B0%5D%5Bcolumns%5D%5B0%5D%5Bblocks%5D%5B0%5D%5Btype%5D=thb_text_box&appearance%5Bwidth%5D=boxed&appearance%5Bpadding_top%5D=&appearance%5Bpadding_bottom%5D=&appearance%5Bmargin_top%5D=-150&appearance%5Bmargin_bottom%5D=&appearance%5Bbackground%5D%5Bid%5